The paper deals with face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model is a Bayesian approach to learning, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions situational context, which could relate to multimedia (cs.MM) and the ability to handle unlabelled data suggests a focus on cryptography and security (cs.CR).
